1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
笙ｪLet me write the legend笙ｪ

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 8=

4
00:00:16,580 --> 00:00:21,180
(Martial Tournament)

5
00:00:21,199 --> 00:00:22,559
After the first round,

6
00:00:22,559 --> 00:00:25,760
six contestants remain.

7
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,800
Everyone, take a short break.

8
00:00:27,839 --> 00:00:28,600
The second round...

9
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:29,440
Dasheng!

10
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:31,320
That move was amazing!

11
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:34,520
Dasheng,

12
00:00:35,119 --> 00:00:36,320
no one does it like you.

13
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:38,399
I had to fight my heart out

14
00:00:38,399 --> 00:00:39,600
just to make it through.

15
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:42,079
Yet you won your match
with a single move.

16
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,840
You're quite the fighter, Mr. Peng.

17
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,880
I'm impressed.

18
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:53,439
(Tang Feng, Heir of Shuzhong Tang Clan)
I'm Tang Feng of the Shuzhong Tang Clan.

19
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:54,920
A pleasure to meet you.

20
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:56,039
Tang Clan people

21
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,799
can sniff out action from miles away.

22
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:00,439
Wherever something's happening,
they're sure to show up.

23
00:01:02,359 --> 00:01:03,520
What brings you here, Feng?

24
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,799
Nothing in particular.

25
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:07,680
I just wanted to warn you, Dasheng.

26
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:11,560
The man beside you is bad news.

27
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,760
Pretty boy,

28
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:18,239
are you looking for trouble?

29
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,239
I'm just telling it like it is.

30
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,120
Why so defensive? Got something to hide?

31
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,719
Dasheng,

32
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:36,920
do those two have some kind of grudge?

33
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:39,439
A grudge?

34
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:41,760
They're sworn enemies.

35
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,159
Everyone, the second round

36
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:50,959
of the martial tournament
is about to begin.

37
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:53,719
This is a weapons round.

38
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:56,879
You may use
whichever weapon suits you best.

39
00:01:56,879 --> 00:02:01,799
You'll draw lots marked Heaven, Earth,
and Man to determine your matchups.

40
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,560
Weapons can be deadly,

41
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,719
so everyone,

42
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:06,400
please show restraint.

43
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:15,860
(Heaven)

44
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,120
Looks like it's you and me.

45
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,120
Let's have a good match.

46
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,759
Mr. Tang!

47
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:25,680
Mr. Tang!

48
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,719
- Mr. Tang!
- Mr. Tang!

49
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,800
Please sign this for me!

50
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,159
He's topped
the Young Hero Heartthrob List

51
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,840
three years running.

52
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:37,439
Mr. Tang
certainly lives up to his reputation.

53
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,759
I heard the top two spots on the list

54
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:42,360
haven't changed in three years.

55
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,439
If Mr. Tang is number one,

56
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,840
who's number two?

57
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,080
As for the runner-up,

58
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,360
he's none other than

59
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,759
Mr. Xiao Ziting,

60
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:53,039
one of today's final six.

61
00:02:57,439 --> 00:03:00,800
Why does this look so familiar?

62
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,520
Dasheng,

63
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:02,919
you're my friend, right?

64
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,240
Why are you asking that all of a sudden?

65
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,439
If you are, don't hold back

66
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:07,080
when you face him.

67
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,879
Find a chance
to mess up that pretty face of his.

68
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,680
Then rob his family shrine
while you're at it.

69
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:13,199
Isn't that going a little too far?

70
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,240
The Tang Clan's
Pear Blossom Needle Storm

71
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,400
is said to strike like a downpour,

72
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,520
swift as the wind.

73
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,680
It certainly lives up to its name.

74
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,560
You're a grown man,

75
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,960
yet you play with sewing needles
all day long.

76
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,879
Aren't you embarrassed?

77
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:58,919
Quit acting so dainty.

78
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,360
Exactly!

79
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,720
What?

80
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,959
Unbelievable.

81
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:25,199
Mr. Peng looks so manly,

82
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:27,399
yet he'd pull a move like that.

83
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,720
I can't unsee that.

84
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:38,759
Stop looking.

85
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
I have your hidden weapons.

86
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,240
The Tang Clan is weakest at close range.

87
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,519
You've lost.

88
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,120
I concede.

89
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:49,340
(Out)

90
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:01,279
At this rate, he could get killed.

91
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:04,800
Told you.

92
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,480
Peng Dasheng.

93
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:06,800
That's enough.

94
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,560
We need to talk in private.

95
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,199
Why can't you say it here?

96
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:20,439
I...

97
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,759
I want you to withdraw
from the tournament.

98
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,959
You're scared Dasheng will win
and make you look bad, aren't you?

99
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,639
Xiaojiu, let's go.

100
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,680
Peng Dasheng!

101
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:45,079
Keep fighting,

102
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,519
and it'll cost you your life.

103
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,519
If he has a death wish,

104
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:54,199
why waste your breath, Bingqing?

105
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,519
Peng Dasheng, let me be clear.

106
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:00,759
You won't walk off

107
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,920
that stage alive.

108
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,160
Lin Dun, what are you planning?

109
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:09,160
You'll find out soon enough.

110
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:19,920
Everyone, we have now reached

111
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:22,399
the most anticipated event
of today's martial tournament,

112
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:25,199
the final showdown!

113
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:25,920
Wait!

114
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,879
I withdraw.

115
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,800
He's withdrawing?

116
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,519
He's withdrawing?

117
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,480
Why would he withdraw?

118
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,439
Yeah, why?

119
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,160
What's he doing?

120
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:35,639
Hold this for me.

121
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:36,920
Exactly!

122
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,959
Dasheng,

123
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:45,160
the rest is up to you.

124
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,800
Next,

125
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:58,759
Peng Dasheng and Lin Dun
will face each other.

126
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,360
There will be no time limit.

127
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,560
The match ends only
when a winner is decided.

128
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:04,279
There is only one rule.

129
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,480
You must both choose your weapons

130
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,319
from the weapon rack,

131
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:12,439
so neither of you
has an unfair advantage.

132
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,839
Let the match begin!

133
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:39,560
Peng Dasheng,
you should leave your last words now.

134
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,319
Don't say later
that I didn't give you the chance.

135
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,399
Lin Dun,

136
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,839
have you forgotten

137
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:47,040
the martial world's rule

138
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,480
that a duel ends
once victory is decided?

139
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,360
Rules?

140
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,079
My father is one of the most powerful
elders in the martial world today.

141
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:55,759
His word is law.

142
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,680
I already said

143
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,000
that if I lose today,

144
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,079
I'll sever my own meridians,

145
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:00,639
cripple my cultivation,

146
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:01,600
and leave the martial world forever.

147
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:03,519
But what happens
if you're the one who loses?

148
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,600
I've trained in martial arts
since I was a child

149
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,199
and mastered my father's techniques.

150
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:09,399
My inner force
has already reached the third level.

151
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:12,120
How could I possibly lose

152
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,240
to a good-for-nothing
with no inner force?

153
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,199
Why dodge the question?

154
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:18,879
Are you scared?

155
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,879
Don't be ridiculous.

156
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:22,240
Well,

157
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,680
swear it

158
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,199
in front of everyone.

159
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:27,160
If you lose today,

160
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:30,360
you'll kneel and bow to me three times.

161
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,040
Do you dare?

162
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,639
(If I back down now,)

163
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,159
(I'll never live it down
in the martial world.)

164
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:38,320
(I can't let this brat)

165
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,960
(shame the Lin family.)

166
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,440
Fine. It's a deal.

167
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,600
But if you lose,

168
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,120
giving up your martial arts
won't be enough.

169
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:52,919
You'll draw your blade
and take your own life

170
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,759
in front of everyone.

171
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:58,559
Today, I won't just beat you.

172
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,600
I'll teach you how to be

173
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,480
a good son in your father's place.

174
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,720
Let's see if you live long enough
to try.

175
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,200
Sir, the weapons have been switched

176
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,240
as you ordered.

177
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,440
Dasheng, watch out!

178
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:55,759
That's strange. Where did he go?
He vanished in a blink.

179
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:58,919
Could this be
the legendary Dongyang ninjutsu?

180
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,279
He uses his surroundings
to conceal himself,

181
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:01,679
then waits for a chance to strike.

182
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:07,660
笙ｪThis battle, I won't retreat笙ｪ

183
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,740
笙ｪI emerge into the world笙ｪ

184
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:12,460
笙ｪUnknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world笙ｪ

185
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:13,900
笙ｪMy pride is my trump card笙ｪ

186
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,660
笙ｪEven if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield笙ｪ

187
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:17,100
笙ｪBorn with a gift, I won't give in笙ｪ

188
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:18,980
笙ｪAgainst heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise笙ｪ

189
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,100
笙ｪA sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain笙ｪ

190
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,140
笙ｪI dare to break every rule笙ｪ

191
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,480
Dasheng,

192
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:25,360
I'll play you a tune and cheer you on.

193
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,500
笙ｪThey kneel and beg for fame笙ｪ

194
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,820
笙ｪI stand and fight for my dignity笙ｪ

195
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:30,340
笙ｪFacing powerful foes, I will not bow笙ｪ

196
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:31,900
笙ｪWith my blade in hand,
I decide what is right笙ｪ

197
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:33,660
笙ｪStand for justice and never step back笙ｪ

198
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:35,020
笙ｪEven if the whole world
stands against me笙ｪ

199
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:36,940
笙ｪUntamed,
frost has carved me to the bone笙ｪ

200
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,039
Unless I'm mistaken,

201
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:40,159
Mr. Lin is using

202
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:42,360
Huxiao Manor's secret technique,

203
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,960
the Mystic Void Finger.

204
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,720
Once mastered,

205
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,200
it can shatter stone from afar.

206
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,879
Its power is incredible.

207
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,660
笙ｪI raise my blade and change my fate笙ｪ

208
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:55,340
笙ｪLet me write the legend笙ｪ

209
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:02,660
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

210
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:06,300
笙ｪOne slash cuts through
the fickle ways of fate笙ｪ

211
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:08,900
笙ｪFrom nothing, I built it all
and bore the weight alone笙ｪ

212
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:12,220
笙ｪEven if the ending
is nothing but desolation笙ｪ

213
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,919
Mr. Lin's inner cultivation
is exceptional,

214
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,480
yet he couldn't withstand
even one move from Peng Dasheng.

215
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,120
Peng Dasheng's sect may be little known,

216
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,919
but his skills are clearly top-tier.

217
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:24,480
He really is
this tournament's dark horse.

218
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,720
Impossible!

219
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,480
That's impossible!

220
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:40,960
Wait.

221
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:43,960
Mr. Lin, you seem to have forgotten

222
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,720
your wager with my young master.

223
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,279
That's right!

224
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,039
Apologize!

225
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:50,720
Yes, apologize!

226
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,480
- Apologize!
- Apologize!

227
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:53,240
Apologize now!

228
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,759
- Apologize!
- Apologize!

229
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,159
That's right!

230
00:11:55,399 --> 00:11:56,200
Fine.

231
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,279
I admit defeat.

232
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,679
Satisfied?

233
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,879
Lin Dun,

234
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,440
after today, we're even.

235
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,799
You'd better watch yourself from now on.

236
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:41,120
(Peng Dasheng, I swear)

237
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:43,440
(I will make you pay for this.)

238
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,120
Everyone,

239
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,919
you all saw what happened.

240
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:56,159
This martial tournament
now has its winner.

241
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:57,279
I hereby declare

242
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:58,240
the winner to be...

243
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,039
Wait!

244
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,559
Peng Dasheng

245
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:05,559
used Dongyang ninjutsu just now,

246
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,480
not our local martial art.

247
00:13:08,279 --> 00:13:10,240
That wasn't a fair win!

248
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,080
Dongyang ninjutsu?

249
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:13,919
He's right! That wasn't fair!

250
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:14,320
What?

251
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,159
Who said

252
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:16,519
I used Dongyang ninjutsu?

253
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,320
Kun Zhongyu,

254
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,639
quit twisting things.

255
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,759
Dasheng comes from the Wuhuduandao Sect.

256
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:25,919
Of course his techniques
come from his own sect.

257
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,639
Right?

258
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:28,399
That makes sense.

259
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:29,360
Esteemed seniors,

260
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,799
have any of you

261
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:31,679
ever heard of a sect

262
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:35,080
called the Wuhuduandao Sect?

263
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,559
As far as I'm concerned,

264
00:13:38,559 --> 00:13:40,840
that sect doesn't even exist.

265
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,799
Peng Dasheng is nothing but a fraud

266
00:13:41,799 --> 00:13:43,039
who steals techniques

267
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:45,320
wherever he goes.

268
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,240
He has a point! A fraud!

269
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:49,120
That's right! A fraud!

270
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:51,000
Don't listen to his lies!

271
00:13:52,679 --> 00:13:54,200
Dasheng is not a fraud!

272
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,879
You say he isn't?

273
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:56,759
Fine.

274
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,240
Show us proof.

275
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:00,240
Go ahead!

276
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,679
That's right! Show us!

277
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:04,039
Where's your proof? Show us!

278
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,399
I'll prove it.

279
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,120
Unless I'm mistaken,

280
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:13,360
isn't that Duan Qingyao,

281
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,679
Holy Maiden of the Wudu Sect?

282
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,480
There's a saying in the martial world:

283
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:19,679
Five steps bring poison;
one smile hides a blade.

284
00:14:19,759 --> 00:14:21,759
It describes her perfectly.

285
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:24,080
With the Holy Maiden
of the Wudu Sect here,

286
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:27,919
things are about to get interesting.

287
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:37,300
笙ｪCome on笙ｪ

288
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:42,500
笙ｪThis battle, I won't retreat笙ｪ

289
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:47,420
笙ｪIn worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust笙ｪ

290
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:50,620
笙ｪAmong the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?笙ｪ

291
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:53,700
笙ｪThey say my birth
has already decided my path笙ｪ

292
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:56,700
笙ｪBut I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth笙ｪ

293
00:14:57,220 --> 00:15:00,180
笙ｪWith one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms笙ｪ

294
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:03,420
笙ｪCovered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless笙ｪ

295
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:06,500
笙ｪIf this world only bows
to status and bloodlines笙ｪ

296
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:09,420
笙ｪThen I'll break every rule
with a single slash笙ｪ

297
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:13,300
笙ｪListen, this heartbeat echoes笙ｪ

298
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:16,340
笙ｪFate is nothing but a net笙ｪ

299
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:22,020
笙ｪEither be trapped by it
or tear it apart笙ｪ

300
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:24,460
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

301
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:27,540
笙ｪI don't believe
anyone is born above another笙ｪ

302
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,660
笙ｪEven this mortal body
dares to fight back笙ｪ

303
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:34,460
笙ｪI'll step on fate and grow beyond it笙ｪ

304
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:37,180
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

305
00:15:38,100 --> 00:15:40,220
笙ｪEven if the world's cold stares
stand in my way笙ｪ

306
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:43,660
笙ｪThis blade will cut through
all worldly judgment笙ｪ

307
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:47,980
笙ｪI am my own king笙ｪ

308
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:02,620
笙ｪI emerge into the world笙ｪ

309
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:04,380
笙ｪUnknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world笙ｪ

310
00:16:04,380 --> 00:16:05,740
笙ｪMy pride is my trump card笙ｪ

311
00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:07,540
笙ｪEven if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield笙ｪ

312
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:08,940
笙ｪBorn with a gift, I won't give in笙ｪ

313
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:10,700
笙ｪAgainst heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise笙ｪ

314
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:12,220
笙ｪA sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain笙ｪ

315
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:13,940
笙ｪI dare to break every rule笙ｪ

316
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:15,260
笙ｪI see through
the masks of human hearts笙ｪ

317
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:17,100
笙ｪFamous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise笙ｪ

318
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,340
笙ｪThey kneel and beg for fame笙ｪ

319
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:20,580
笙ｪI stand and fight for my dignity笙ｪ

320
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,100
笙ｪFacing powerful foes, I will not bow笙ｪ

321
00:16:22,100 --> 00:16:23,700
笙ｪWith my blade in hand,
I decide what is right笙ｪ

322
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:25,300
笙ｪStand for justice and never step back笙ｪ

323
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,020
笙ｪEven if the whole world
stands against me笙ｪ

324
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,740
笙ｪUntamed,
frost has carved me to the bone笙ｪ

325
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:30,100
笙ｪOnly then do I become more like myself笙ｪ

326
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:31,740
笙ｪFight, this life of mine is unyielding笙ｪ

327
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:33,220
笙ｪNo matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it笙ｪ

328
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:34,940
笙ｪFor love, I do not fight for the world笙ｪ

329
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:36,540
笙ｪI only want
to protect her for a lifetime笙ｪ

330
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:38,100
笙ｪCarefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay笙ｪ

331
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:42,420
笙ｪNow I know all things can be overcome笙ｪ

332
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:44,580
笙ｪI raise my blade and change my fate笙ｪ

333
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:47,180
笙ｪLet me write the legend笙ｪ

334
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:54,620
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

335
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:57,940
笙ｪWin or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me笙ｪ

336
00:16:57,940 --> 00:17:00,420
笙ｪEven if I fall, I will still shine笙ｪ

337
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:04,500
笙ｪLet my name
be carved into the vast world笙ｪ

338
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:07,460
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

339
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:09,940
笙ｪIf this world refuses to forgive me笙ｪ

340
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:12,980
笙ｪThen I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance笙ｪ

341
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:18,020
笙ｪAnd trade it for a new dawn笙ｪ
